                    <h1>Transfer<br /> Students</h1>
                    <h3>From Amarillo<br  />College Find a<br /> Home at</h3>
                    <h2>Texas Tech</h2>
                    <p><em><small>by Rachel Blevins, photo courtesy Russell Lowery-Hart</small></em></p>
